description: This common Cooter purrs with a rating of 30, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 60, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Stringalong for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [60 Votes, Common]
